OL,3,CCyclist, 85, dies after coming off
OL,4,Cbike before collision with car
OL,6,FA cyclist has died following a
OL,7,Fcollision in Hayling Island.
OL,9,FPolice received reports that a man had
OL,10,Fcome off his bike before being
OL,11,Finvolved in a collision with a red
OL,12,FFord Fiesta on the Langstone Road
OL,13,Fbridge at around 12:30pm on Thursday.
OL,14,F(9 April)
OL,16,FThe cyclist, an 85-year-old man from
OL,17,FHayling Island was serious injured and
OL,18,Ftaken to the QA Hospital in Portsmouth.
OL,20,FHe died a short time later.
