OL,3,CCyclist, 85, dies after coming off
OL,4,Cbike before collision with car
OL,6,FPolice say the man's next of kin are
OL,7,Faware.
OL,9,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,10,F"We urge anyone who witnessed this
OL,11,Fincident, or perhaps captured it on
OL,12,FDash Cam, to call police on 101
OL,13,Fquoting 44260165380."
